; Multi-currency Beancount File
; Testing currency conversion with @ and @@

2014-01-01 open Assets:US:BofA:Checking USD
2014-01-01 open Assets:FR:SocGen:Checking EUR
2014-01-01 open Assets:US:Vanguard:Cash USD
2014-01-01 open Liabilities:CreditCard:CapitalOne USD
2014-01-01 open Income:US:Salary
2014-01-01 open Expenses:Travel

; Simple USD transaction
2014-02-01 * "Grocery store"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -50.00 USD
  Expenses:Food:Groceries  50.00 USD

; Currency conversion with per-unit price (@)
; Convert 400 USD to CAD at 1.09 rate
2014-02-03 * "Transfer to account in Canada"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -400.00 USD @ 1.09 CAD
  Assets:FR:SocGen:Checking  436.00 CAD

; Currency conversion with total price (@@)
; Convert 500 USD to EUR at total 365 EUR
2014-02-05 * "Transfer to France"
  Assets:US:BofA:Checking  -500.00 USD @@ 365.00 EUR
  Assets:FR:SocGen:Checking  365.00 EUR

; Stock purchase in USD showing cost basis
2014-02-10 * "US stocks purchase"
  Assets:US:Vanguard:Cash  -5000.00 USD
  Assets:US:Vanguard:IVV  25 IVV {200.00 USD}
  Expenses:Investments  5000.00 USD

; Credit card in USD
2014-02-15 * "Amazon purchase"
  Liabilities:CreditCard:CapitalOne  -76.00 USD
  Expenses:Shopping  76.00 USD

; Price directive for setting currency conversion rate
2014-03-01 price USD 1.09 CAD
2014-03-01 price USD 0.73 EUR